<p>A simple network is simple, but what happens when you need to do a little more? What are the potential pitfalls of storing Photos and iTunes libraries on your network drive? Want to make snapshots before you upgrade? All of this and more on today&#39;s Mac Geek Gab with Dave Hamilton, John F. Braun and Pilot Pete!</p>
